title: Manafort, Rocket Man and the New GOP Health Care Bill: A Closer Look | Gilbert Gottfried
description:
Seth takes a closer look at how the GOP is trying to ram through a plan to repeal and replace Obamacare while waiting for what could be the Russia investigation's first indictment.
Then, Seth talks to legendary comedian Gilbert Gottfried about the new documentary he stars in, "Gilbert." Gottfried also takes a few more questions backstage with Late Night producer Kevin Miller.
